/*
 * Linky, text forwarder 
 */
- install on 2 phones
- have phones relay texts back and forth to eachother.
- 2 components:
	- listener
		- listens for incoming texts
		- intercepts
		- sends modified copy to receiving phone containing original message + sender phone number
		- allows texts to continue to Messaging app
	- receiver
		- listens for texts received from listening phone
		- intercepts
		- parses out original sender phone number and message
		- sends reparsed message to Messaging app with data as if it came directly from original sender
		- intercepts outgoing 
